--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
11.13 SPECIFIC REFACTORING KEYWORDS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
KEYWORD           | WHAT IT DOES
------------------|--------------------------------------
"Extract Method"  | Move chunk to new helper function
"Inline"          | Put small function back into caller
"De-couple"       | Break dependency between components
"Extract Class"   | Move related methods to new class
"Rename"          | Change names for clarity
"Move Method"     | Relocate method to better class


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
11.14 DATA STRUCTURE KEYWORDS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
STRUCTURE         | USE CASE                   | TIME COMPLEXITY
------------------|----------------------------|-------------------------
"HashMap/Dict"    | Fast key-value lookup      | O(1)
"Array/List"      | Ordered sequence           | O(n) search, O(1) index
"Set"             | Unique items, fast lookup  | O(1)
"Queue (FIFO)"    | First-in-first-out         | O(1)
"Stack (LIFO)"    | Last-in-first-out          | O(1)
"Tree"            | Hierarchical data          | O(log n) balanced
"Graph"           | Networks, relationships    | Varies
"Heap"            | Priority queue             | O(log n)


